    <content>&lt;P class=""&gt;Hi everyone,&lt;BR /&gt;I'm encountering an issue when trying to connect to an OData service in SAP. The error message I'm getting is:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;"The OData or EDMX specification file was not found at the destination."&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;I can see this issue when trying to &lt;STRONG&gt;add a new action&lt;/STRONG&gt; using the OData integration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Hossam_Fathy_0-1744101970454.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/247978i7B1C0E1F211A1A3E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Hossam_Fathy_0-1744101970454.png" alt="Hossam_Fathy_0-1744101970454.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I’ve already checked the destination configuration in SAP BTP and verified the URL.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Hossam_Fathy_1-1744102010722.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/247979i930DA0C2C89C92E1/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Hossam_Fathy_1-1744102010722.png" alt="Hossam_Fathy_1-1744102010722.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;Has anyone faced this issue before? What could be the possible reasons or steps to resolve it?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;Any help or guidance would be appreciated.&lt;BR /&gt;Thanks in advance!&lt;/P&gt;</content>
